---
import ServicePage from '../../components/ServicePage.astro';
---
<ServicePage
	title="in Clapham"
	highlight="Pilates"
	breadcrumb="Pilates"
	seoTitle="Pilates in Clapham"
	seoDescription="Pilates classes and one-to-one studio sessions in Clapham, London. Run by Pilates Sanctuary in partnership with Balance Performance Physiotherapy."
	hideMarquee
	intro={[
		"At Balance we are incredibly fortunate to work right alongside Pilates Sanctuary, who run a fully equipped Pilates studio on the first floor of our Clapham facility. We have done so for many years.",
		"Pilates is an excellent practice for many of our clients within the process of rehabilitation, especially when it comes to recovery from episodes of back and neck pain. The Pilates Sanctuary team have a fantastic eye for movement, spotting inaccuracies and imbalances and then working on them with precision and patience until awareness and control are achieved.",
		"Our own movement team work concurrently with Pilates Sanctuary so clients can connect Pilates mat and machine work with the movement patterns of their day-to-day life, sport, endurance and outdoor activities.",
	]}
	whenHeading="When to consider"
	whenHighlight="Pilates"
	whenIntro="Through a series of adaptable exercises on the mat and on specialised equipment, Pilates focuses on creating:"
	whenList={[
		"A stable centre",
		"Joint mobility and stability",
		"A fluid, elongated spine",
		"Flowing, functional movement",
		"Dynamic strength and flexibility",
	]}
	whenOutro="All of which work to restore the body to balance and to good functional movement, whoever you are."
	howHeading="How studio"
	howHighlight="sessions work"
	howIntro="Pilates Sanctuary have a fully equipped studio on the first floor of our Clapham facility. Studio work uses spring-resistance equipment alongside mat work, with sessions tailored to your needs."
	howList={[
		"Individual assessment with a programme developed for your needs",
		"Smaller groups of up to 5 people, so you get more individual attention",
		"Improvements to posture, breath, and full-body movement",
		"Spring resistance lets you target areas more specifically and work with more load",
		"A greater repertoire of exercises and a more adaptable approach for different conditions",
		"Appropriate at all stages of pregnancy",
	]}
	howOutro="<strong>Group sessions</strong> are up to 5 people. Private sessions are also available. All sessions last one hour. If you are coming because of an injury or have a particular issue to address, an initial private session may be required before you join group classes."
	whoHeading="Who Pilates"
	whoHighlight="is for"
	whoIntro="Studio work is for absolutely everyone, from complete beginners and people recovering from injury through to athletes and dancers. Established in 2006, Pilates Sanctuary specialises in:"
	whoList={[
		"Rehabilitation",
		"Maternity care and women's health",
		"Working with dancers",
		"Older members of the Clapham community",
		"Wellbeing and fitness",
	]}
	faqs={[
		{ q: "How do I book?", a: "All classes must be booked in advance. Call one of the Pilates Sanctuary Directors directly: Agur on 07824 901 063 or Alice on 07881 953 843." },
		{ q: "How big are the groups?", a: "Group sessions have up to 5 people. You can also do private sessions in the studio. All sessions last one hour." },
		{ q: "Do I need an initial private session?", a: "If you are coming because of an injury or have a particular issue you need addressing, we may ask you to have an initial private session before joining group classes." },
		{ q: "When do classes run?", a: "Studio sessions take place Monday to Friday." },
		{ q: "What does it cost?", a: "Private sessions are £85 for a single session or £420 for a block of 5. Group sessions are £40 for a single session or £195 for a block of 5." },
		{ q: "Is Pilates suitable during pregnancy?", a: "Yes. The studio approach is appropriate at all stages of pregnancy and Pilates Sanctuary specialise in maternity care and women's health." },
		{ q: "Who do I contact with general enquiries?", a: "For general Balance enquiries, email admin@balancephysio.com or call 020 7627 2308. For Pilates-specific bookings, contact Agur or Alice directly on the numbers above." },
	]}
>
	<div slot="before-faq" class="container" style="padding-top: 32px;">
		<div class="image-text-content" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
			<div class="eyebrow">Booking</div>
			<h2>Book a session at <span class="highlight">Pilates Sanctuary</span></h2>
			<p>To book a session of one-to-one teaching or join a small group, call one of the Pilates Sanctuary Directors directly:</p>
			<p><strong>Agur:</strong> <a href="tel:+447824901063">07824 901 063</a><br/>
			<strong>Alice:</strong> <a href="tel:+447881953843">07881 953 843</a></p>
			<p>For general Balance enquiries: <a href="mailto:admin@balancephysio.com">admin@balancephysio.com</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</ServicePage>
